      section#aboutMe(data-sr="enter bottom, move 16px")
        h2 About me
        .container
          p I guess you have figured out that I like comics. Here is a bit more about me..
          p I was born in Shillong, a beautiful city located in the North-Eastern state of Meghalaya. I spent my younger days playing and roaming in its streets, and then I moved to Bangalore - now known as Bengaluru. But not before I developed a keen interest in design.
          p When I came to Bangalore, priorities changed and I started working in a MNC. Then I changed a few jobs, till the time I got one where I joined as a designer. Previously all were IT related jobs but once I started designing, I realized that I was working at the wrong places! Soon after that, I learned the skills required to become a competant web designer and in the process I learnt about web development as well.
          p Now after a few years of learning, I think I can say I make pretty cool websites. I personally like to believe this is one of them :P


